blackjack.c   written by Raymond Wong.
Rules:
  1. Dealer has to take hits until his/her cards total 17 or more points.
  2. Player has two options: hit, stand.
  3. Ace is always counted as 1 point.
  

blackjack1.c   Changed by me.
Added Rules:
  1. Ace is counted as 1 or 11 point. (Always counted as the optimal points.)
  
  
